      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "I'M HONEY (4) made light work of the tricky draw with a fast early sectional but gathered in and had to settle for the minors, finishing third (23.60) at Horsham over 410m. Can find winning form. MORAINE QUINN (1) was below best at her last start when 6th at Ballarat following a win (25.92) at this track two back. Goes well out of this box with a win and five minor placings. One of the better chances. PENNY PINTO (2) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 4.5 lengths at this track in a handy 22.43 beating Inga Amy. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Has definite claims. SICILY (8) has a solid strike rate from this box.",
